data.description: *MASSIVE PRICE REDUCTION* Income producing property brining in $2000/month. Motivated seller! Investor Special & currently rented out to a tenant! Come check out this REMODELED single family 4 bedroom/2 bathroom 2 story home in Jacksonville, Florida. Seller has put over $60,000 in upgrades over the last year (New pool pump & pool water, new double pane hurricane proof windows, flooring vents covered, new ducts and upgraded HVAC system, new fence, new redone stairwell & more). This beautiful remodeled property is currently renting for BELOW market rent & great for any investor who wants to bring it to market rent. This property is a great starter home for a family as well. Property is currently occupied and tenants will need a minimum of 24 hours notice for all showings.
